N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 205.7 - Identification of a fire mobilization and mutual aid zone

State Regulations
A "zone" as used in the statutes is a "county" as
determined by the State Constitution. Those counties comprising the City of New

York are constituted as a single zone. Notes
